## 5. Kesimpulan QA Design Baru

**Kekuatan:**
- Workflow selaras **Excel Spartan** (8 area vs 4 wizard ERP)
- Engine COGS, parity audit, export multi-sheet
- UX material picker + nominal color + nama sync master

**Kelemahan vs ERP production:**
- Master masih **dummy lokal**, belum DB ERP terpusat
- Belum auth multi-user / approval workflow ERP
- Beberapa kolom placeholder (stock, status material)

